            "description": "Get latest payment from mock API.\n\nExpected: 200 OK with payment data."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "FoodMarket Order Summary (GET - Complex Mapping)",
      "description": "FoodMarket mock API - a food delivery order system.\n\nRaw API returns complex nested order with 8 items, payment breakdown, delivery info.\nProxy mapping transforms it into a simple summary with category counts and totals.\n\nMapping ID: e5555555-5555-5555-5555-555555555555\nAuth: Bearer token (handled by proxy)\nRaw endpoint: GET /api/foodmarket/orders/{orderId}\nProxy endpoint: GET /api/proxy/e5555555-5555-5555-5555-555555555555",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "🔄 PROXY: Get Order Summary (mapped response)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "X-Tenant-Id", "value": "{{tenantId}}" }
            ],
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}/api/proxy/{{foodmarketMappingId}}",
            "description": "Calls FoodMarket API through the proxy.\n\nThe proxy:\n1. Calls GET /api/foodmarket/orders/ORD-5001 with Bearer auth\n2. Applies JSONata transformation (aggregation, flattening, calculation)\n3. Returns simplified summary\n\nExpected mapped response:\n{\n  orderId, customerName, customerLoyalty, restaurantName,\n  totalItems: 13 (sum of all quantities),\n  totalAmount: 96.29, currency: TRY,\n  foodCount: 4, beverageCount: 6, dessertCount: 2, snackCount: 1,\n  deliveryMinutes: 22, onTime: true, overallRating: 4.5\n}"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "📋 RAW: Get Order (full response - before mapping)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer demo-token-12345" }
            ],
            "url": "{{mockApiUrl}}/api/foodmarket/orders/ORD-5001",
            "description": "Direct call to FoodMarket mock API - returns the FULL complex response.\n\nCompare this with the proxy response above to see the transformation.\n\nResponse includes:\n- 8 items across 4 categories (FOOD x4qty, BEVERAGE x6qty, DESSERT x2qty, SNACK x1qty)\n- Nested customer with loyalty tier (GOLD) and address\n- Payment breakdown (subtotal 85.93, tax 6.87, delivery 4.99, tip 3.50, discount -5.00 = total 96.29 TRY)\n- Delivery driver info (22 min actual vs 25 min estimated)\n- Ratings (food:5, delivery:4, overall:4.5)"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "📋 RAW: Get Different Order",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer demo-token-12345" }
            ],
            "url": "{{mockApiUrl}}/api/foodmarket/orders/ORD-9999",
            "description": "Direct call with different order ID to verify dynamic data."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "❌ RAW: Without Auth (401)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": "{{mockApiUrl}}/api/foodmarket/orders/ORD-5001",
            "description": "Direct call without Bearer token.\n\nExpected: 401 Unauthorized.\nThe proxy handles auth automatically - you don't need to provide it."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "📋 RAW: List Orders",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer demo-token-12345" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{mockApiUrl}}/api/foodmarket/orders?limit=3",
              "host": ["{{mockApiUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "foodmarket", "orders"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "limit", "value": "3" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "List multiple orders from mock API."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
